Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.95,0:02:51.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setiap bintang di langit,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu sebenarnya bayi-bayi kecil.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.46,0:02:57.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka itu, akan pilih\Nayah dan ibu mereka sendiri,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu turun dari langit\Ndatang ke sisi mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.85,0:03:02.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dulu juga bintang di langit?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.75,0:03:05.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.58,0:03:10.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang memilih Ayah dan Mama,\Nbaru kita jadi satu keluarga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.83,0:03:14.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.33,0:03:16.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah datang ke Mama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah jadi anak Mama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku masih tidak paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar ibumu istirahat sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sana main sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu Ayah temani aku main.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku masih mau main bumerang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.54,0:03:32.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke, oke.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shh.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.75,0:03:38.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Little Johnny,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,jangan berisik, Ayahmu lagi telepon.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mama akan ceritakan satu cerita lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.12,0:03:43.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.95,0:03:48.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Shang,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.08,0:03:49.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku akan menyelidikinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.54,0:03:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat lakukan resusitasi jantung paru.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.95,0:04:00.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.00,0:04:08.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Little Johnny,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.87,0:04:09.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mama bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.37,0:04:14.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Shang sudah mengirimkan\Ntim medis paling canggih kemari.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kecepatan kondisinya memburuk\Njauh lebih cepat dari yang kita duga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.29,0:04:18.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar aku yang lakukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.70,0:04:20.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.83,0:04:21.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah Sheng, semuanya lancar?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, lancar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, kau jangan cemberut terus.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.16,0:04:42.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua nanti harus bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita bertiga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan biarkan kau pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun agak berat hati,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.13,0:04:53.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau tetap bawa Little Johnny\Npergi dari sini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Papa,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.62,0:05:33.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,belum tidur?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.58,0:05:47.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau lari ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasakan bumerang ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia bayi yang kubawa pulang\Nsaat menjalankan misi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau di luar punya bayi lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia juga tidak kelihatan mirip.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu ia dari mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Detailnya aku juga tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi bisa dipastikan,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,ia bukan makhluk dari planet kita ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan ia jatuh dari langit?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa dibilang begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beberapa hari lalu, ada pesawat luar angkasa\Njatuh di zona tak berpenghuni.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menemukannya saat sedang menyelidiki.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.87,0:06:29.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya ia satu-satunya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, hanya ia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Khawatir kalau ia ditemukan orang lain,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin akan dijadikan bahan penelitian\Natau bahkan dilukai.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, aku membawanya pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu ia siapa,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,dari mana asalnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia anakku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mama yang bilang padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.66,0:07:01.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bayi-bayi kecil itu semua turun dari langit\Ndatang ke sisi papa dan mama mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ia juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Coba lihat, kita berdua mirip banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.87,0:07:09.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku Little Johnny.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu kuberi nama kau
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daqiang saja, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.95,0:07:13.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daqiang,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,kuajak kau lihat lingkungan baru dulu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.87,0:07:21.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nak,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,nenekmu pernah bilang padaku,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,minum susu cepat besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.85,0:07:25.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habiskan semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti kau sembunyi di dalam tas sekolah,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,diam-diam jangan bersuara.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dan Kakek mau bawa kau ke rumah baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Liftnya sudah datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat kemari.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.08,0:07:48.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau sungguh
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.41,0:07:50.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,mau pergi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah diputuskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh tidak mau pikir-pikir lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini anakmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru pertama kali ketemu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai X,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,banyak sekali yang harus kau pedulikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Identitas pahlawan yang susah payah\Ndidapat juga dilepas begitu saja,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak sayang?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pahlawan juga buat apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada akhirnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tetap tidak bisa menyelamatkan dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah insiden jatuhnya fajar,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.58,0:08:24.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang-orang tidak akan lagi kasih kita\Nkekuatan melebihi dewa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pasti bukan datang\Nhanya untuk pedulikan aku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.86,0:08:30.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat menghargai masa pensiun\Nyang susah payah ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.66,0:08:36.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah mencapai lantai dasar Menara Pahlawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.04,0:08:36.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Papa,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita mau ke mana sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke tempat di mana tidak ada yang kenal kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.41,0:08:58.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nak, cepat diam.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan cuci mukaku lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini rumah baru kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bengong.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat bantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nak, lihat baik-baik, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.45,0:09:28.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Basahi dulu,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.12,0:09:30.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,terus seperti ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,biar tiap lantai bisa disapu bersih.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.08,0:09:38.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paham?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.95,0:09:39.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sini, coba kau.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.87,0:09:41.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bodoh!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu air buat mengepel.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak boleh diminum.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak durhaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.54,0:09:54.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau lari ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.00,0:09:58.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pelnya bagaimana...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iblis, enyahlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iblis, enyahlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bukan kakekmu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia itu iblis pel yang kena sihir.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.95,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Iblis, enyahlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak durhaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau lari ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iblis, enyahlah! Iblis, enyahlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.37,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Iblis, enyahlah! Iblis, enyahlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.75,0:10:17.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapan rumah ini mulai dihuni orang?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.62,0:10:19.50,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Iblis, enyahlah! Iblis, enyahlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.91,0:10:18.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada hantu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benda sekotor ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.58,0:10:35.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,kenapa dibuang ke sungai?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dosa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dosa besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.90,0:10:41.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hantu berkeliaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.91,0:10:44.95,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Cepat pulang ke rumah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.95,0:10:45.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Celana dalamku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat berhenti.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mama,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daqiang nakal banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.62,0:11:21.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu aku kecil, apa aku juga kayak dia,\Nbikin Mama kesal?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau itu jauh lebih nakal dari Daqiang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sering banget bikin ibumu marah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi Mama selalu senyum, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.16,0:11:31.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah ibumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia menipu semua orang dengan senyumnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,termasuk aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibumu sering bilang,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,kesedihan tidak bisa menyembuhkan luka,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,apalagi jadi obat pembangkit orang mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi itu membuat kita ingat,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa yang benar-benar kita pedulikan di hati,\Napa yang kita butuhkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.16,0:11:52.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,saatnya menangis,\Nmenangislah sekeras-kerasnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi setelah menangis,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,jangan lupa senyum adalah kekuatan\Nuntuk melanjutkan harapan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak durhaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.99,0:12:17.82,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Muntahkan itu!\NItu buat nenekmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.75,0:12:23.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat jurusku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Roda Angin Tak Terkalahkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.00,0:12:26.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sip.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tertangkap!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pasti yang orang dewasa\Nbilang "makhluk jahat" itu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.81,0:12:38.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini apaan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kalian sedang apa?\N- Kucing putih besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.75,0:12:41.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati-hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.48,0:12:44.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia anakku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.67,0:12:45.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian tidak boleh sentuh dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bilang apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.08,0:12:48.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bilang itu anaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan dia gila, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan banyak omong sama dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengar-dengar ia dari kota.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang dewasa semua bilang,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang kota otaknya pada bermasalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian yang sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daqiang itu anakku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mendekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya kau tergoda\Nsama makhluk jahat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian jangan mendekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.04,0:13:08.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minggir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mumpung sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar kalian penakut.\NIni kan hanya...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,kucing kecil biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.04,0:13:34.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daqiang,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,tak disangka kau sekuat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, harus dilatih baik-baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.54,0:13:57.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti jadi pahlawan besar kayak kakekmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai ayah, kenapa tidak jadi contoh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kebiasaan Daqiang yang makannya lahap\Nitu gara-gara kau.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Utamanya, sih,\Nkarena masakan Ayah enak banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daqiang, benar atau tidak?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku buka pintu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Little Johnny.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau dan Daqiang beresi meja dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.70,0:14:59.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuci yang kotor.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.62,0:15:05.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lama tidak berjumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa kau kemari?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiga tahun tidak bertemu,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagaimana kehidupan di gunung?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saking bagusnya, aku sampai lupa
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,semua masa lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terlalu sensitif.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sengaja mau mengetesmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.12,0:15:33.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan tegang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dengan sifatmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau tidak akan datang kalau tidak ada perlu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Basa-basi sepertinya tidak usah, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang kau yang paling pahami aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku butuh kau.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, aku harap kau bisa kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,pertandingan peringkat sebelumnya\Nkau mengalahkannya,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu berarti kau sudah menemukan cara\Nuntuk mengalahkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.12,0:15:59.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kedua,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku sudah pensiun begitu lama,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,sudah tidak punya kemampuan\Nseperti dulu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.87,0:16:04.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa membantumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu kematiannya sangat memukulmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi selama masih ada orang\Nyang ingat siapa kau,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.12,0:16:13.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau masih bisa menyembuhkan segala sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu sendiri,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau tidak percaya pada diri sendiri,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.30,0:16:19.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,seberapa banyak pun\NNilai Kepercayaan orang lain,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu hanya sekumpulan angka\Nyang tidak berguna.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.70,0:16:25.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dulu tidak suka sifatmu\Nyang tidak mau maju ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal punya potensi sebagus itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.66,0:16:28.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,kenapa harus disia-siakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau khawatir aku akan terbuang,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,atau kau khawatir tentang dirimu sendiri?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak memikirkan dirimu sendiri,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi harus memikirkan anakmu juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.07,0:16:41.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak perlu mengancamku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru sebaliknya,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,akulah ancaman terbesar bagimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perlu tidak aku bantu sembuhkan lukamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.67,0:16:52.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih teh sorenya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.75,0:16:56.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati-hati di jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.87,0:17:07.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutmu, kakekmu dan orang itu\Nada hubungan apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus orang itu siapa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.29,0:17:11.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata ayahmu dulu pahlawan besar di kota.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah Sheng, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian akhirnya datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat bawa barangnya sini, biar aku lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini aku yang ngotot\Nikut papa dan mama ke kota,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,diam-diam kubawa pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Coba lihat,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,komik ini semua ceritakan kisah ayahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata ayahmu punya kemampuan\Nmenyembuhkan segala sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, kenapa dulu dia\Ntidak bisa menyelamatkan ibumu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong yang betul, malah ungkit-ungkit\Nyang bikin orang sedih.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kami juga lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang kau bilang siapa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang tadi datang ke rumahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.16,0:17:55.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.87,0:17:58.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sekarang pahlawan peringkat satu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kulihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.70,0:18:06.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu X yang sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.12,0:18:08.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,X sore-sore ada di rumahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.95,0:18:10.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bikin kaget banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kenapa orang tuaku sering bilang,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.56,0:18:16.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalian para pahlawan dari kota itu\Nmonster pembawa sial?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daqiang, ayo kita pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kok tiba-tiba pergi?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.99,0:18:41.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,jejak setelah bertarung.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.02,0:19:11.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.76,0:19:28.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa orang itu yang melakukannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan selidiki sampai tuntas.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan balaskan dendammu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.70,0:20:10.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daqiang?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daqiang, cepat berhenti!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.03,0:20:44.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.21,0:20:47.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,apakah Daqiang?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar keluarga dari kota itu\Nyang bawa monster ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu X.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.85,0:21:34.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu Pahlawan Vortex.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.58,0:21:38.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.95,0:21:39.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.70,0:21:41.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.08,0:21:42.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu ulahnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.33,0:21:51.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar orang tak tahu diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti setelah aku kalahkan kau,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,baru kubawa pulang\Nke Asosiasi untuk diteliti.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.64,0:22:00.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini kemampuan pahlawan,\Nmenyatukan semua benda jadi pusaran!
